<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>ArgumentParser does not clear
{{$_argumentsWorking}}
after parsing the arguments with Zend_Console_Getopt.</p>

<p>This causes the parse() method to show a help message and stop the application.</p>

<p>however ignoring side effects and setting
{{$this_argumentsWorking = array()}}
at the end of
{{_parseProviderOptionsPart()}}
does solve the problem and the correct parameter is given to my provider.</p>

<p>Using PHP 5.3. Beta 1 and standard incubator from SVN on Mac OS X 10.4 shell:</p>

<p>{{# zf show version --mode=mini}}
{{Unknown arguments left on the command line: --mode=mini}}</p>

<p>Happend with own providers as well.</p>

